author: Disney
description:
In celebration of Predator: Badlands, we hunted down some iconic props from Walt Disney Archives to show Elle Fanning! We reunited Elle with costume pieces from Maleficent: Mistress of Evil and The Great—plus, she got an up-close look at a Yaujta helmet.

Stream Maleficent: Mistress of Evil on Disney+ and The Predator and all episodes of The Great on Hulu.

See Predator: Badlands in theaters now!
